content:
COVERAGE:
Cigna is responsible for the payment of: 100% of thehospital charges and 96% of the professional fees. The patient is responsible for the following: 4% ofthe professional fees
EXCLUSIONS:
Patient convenience items (e.g., television, telephone, extras, etc.); Cosmetictreatments; expenses for Robot surgery (unless authorized prior to surgery); Preventivemedication; Spa cures; Reversal of sterilization; Transport to a secondfacility or transport enabling follow-up visits or outpatient treatmentsessions; Expenses for surgical or laser treatment for the correction ofrefraction are covered up to 250 USD only.
To obtain a settlement, please submit the final itemized invoice(s) within 6 months after the service(s) to bills@cigna.com
Contacts for questions regarding: Payment: providerquestions@cigna.com Eligibility & Benefits: authorization@cigna.com
Or call us at the number on the customer's ID card.
Best regards, Cigna Global Health Benefits
